column1: # This data has been collected by a Texas Water Development Board datasonde.
# Raw data may contain errors. Provisional data has had anomalous
# individual data points removed. Such data points typically are disconnected
# from the recorded trend. Nonetheless all removed data is retained in database.
# However data that simply appear unusual are not removed unless verifying
# information is obtained suggesting the data is not representative of bay conditions.
# The Board makes no warranties (including no warranties as to merchantability or fitness) either
